			<h1>PERSONO</h1>
			<h3>A coffee table that allows the ultimate flexibility of usage. Share it easily among few people or use it for your own private & personal use.</h3>
		</header>
		<section>
			<span class="project-step-number">01</span>
			<h2>CHALLENGE</h2>
			<p>Design a coffee table to be used at home for different usage scenarios. A table that can be easily shared by a group of people or in situations when multiple people want to use the table for their own personal and private needs at the same time.</p>
			<img src="../images/persono-01-research.jpg" alt="Persono Research" title="Persono Research">
